  <data key="d4">core_obligation</data>
  <data key="d5">0.85</data>
  <data key="d6">The controller shall take appropriate measures to provide any information referred to in Articles 13 and 14 and any communication under Articles 15 to 22 and 34 relating to processing to the data subj</data>
