  <data key="d0">rule</data>
  <data key="d8">GDPR_Art54_R7</data>
  <data key="d9">Member or members and staff of each supervisory authority</data>
  <data key="d10">be subject to a duty of professional secrecy both during and after their term of office</data>
  <data key="d11">with regard to any confidential information which has come to their knowledge in the course of the performance of their tasks or exercise of their powers</data>
  <data key="d12">obligation</data>
