  <data key="d9">supervisory authority</data>
  <data key="d10">shall forward that opinion or decision to the court</data>
  <data key="d11">when proceedings are brought against a decision of a supervisory authority which was preceded by an opinion or a decision of the Board in the consistency mechanism</data>
