  <data key="d13">Chapter V on the transfer of personal data to third countries or international organisations with particular regard to decisions adopted pursuant to Article 45(3) of this Regulation and decisions adopted on the basis of Article 25(6) of Directive 95/46/EC; Chapter VII on cooperation and consistency.</data>
  <data key="d2">GDPR</data>
