  <data key="d10">submit appropriate proposals to amend this Regulation</data>
  <data key="d11">if necessary</data>
  <data key="d12">administrative</data>
  <data key="d13">in particular taking into account of developments in information technology and in the light of the state of progress in the information society.</data>
