  <data key="d0">rule</data>
  <data key="d8">EPRIVACY_Art13_R2_1</data>
  <data key="d9">&lt;same natural or legal person&gt;</data>
  <data key="d10">use electronic contact details for direct marketing of its own similar products or services</data>
  <data key="d11">customers have given their electronic contact details in the context of the sale of a product or a service, and customers clearly and distinctly are given the opportunity to object to such use</data>
