  <data key="d10">send electronic mail for the purposes of direct marketing which disguise or conceal the identity of the sender on whose behalf the communication is made, or contravene</data>
  <data key="d11"></data>
  <data key="d12">prohibition</data>
  <data key="d13">&lt;electronic mail&gt;</data>
